Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.76,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}ato dore kurai no sayonara wo nagashitara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:49.56,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}mabuta no oku no izumi ga karehateru, to ka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.27,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sen nengo mo kitto tsuzuku darou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.07,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sou omotteta kuudou wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.65,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}mitashite afurete shimau hodo no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.37,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}kono kimochi wa nan da?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:02.87,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}tanjun da yo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.83,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}maiasa no “ohayou”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.24,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}eiga mitai ni aoi natsu no umi wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}tooi tokoro de ibasho wo shiri
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.04,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}ima to ima wo kasaneteku, firumu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}nankai mo torinaoshi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.54,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}iroaseru yori, irodoru yori, kimi no iru keshiki ga koi na
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.84,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}chokkande mo tossa demo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.55,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sou omottan da, tada mayoi naku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.97,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}shinjitemo ii ka to kikareta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.55,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}tatta sore dake no toi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.09,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}kangaeterun da, donna toki mo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.43,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}ano koe ga tsukimatoi nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.76,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}oshiteru, zutto senaka wo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.35,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sou ka, kono kimochi ga koi da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.32,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sennen mae no tomoshibi ni nobashita nipon no yubi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.37,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}sen nengo mo zutto mukou de kagayaiteru to ii na
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.95,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}“shinjitemo ii” sou kikoeta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.45,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}manmaru na tsuki, aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.75,Kara-Romaji,OP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}terashiteta, itsu no yo mo
